text: Moritz Thiem (born 8 December 1999) is an Austrian tennis player. Thiem has a career high ATP singles ranking of 1294 achieved on 9 September 2019. Thiem made his ATP main draw debut at the 2019 Generali Open Kitzbühel in the doubles draw partnering Nicolás Massú. He is the younger brother of fellow tennis player Dominic Thiem. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male tennis players
